video.title: Power Rangers Dino Thunder
video.synopsis: Dr. Tommy Oliver returns when his students discover the Dino Gems that morph them into the Dino Power Rangers, enabling them to stop the evil Mesogog.

episodes.synopsis: When Mesogog unleashes deadly Bio Zords, former Power Ranger Tommy Oliver recruits three high school kids to become Power Rangers and tame the beasts.
episodes.title: Day of the Dino: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: When Mesogog releases his Bio Zords on the city, Tommy has no choice but to give Dino Morphers to three teens to turn them into Power Rangers.
episodes.title: Day of the Dino: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Conner's given a shot at playing professional soccer, but his Ranger duties impede upon this once-in-a-lifetime chance.
episodes.title: Wave Goodbye

episodes.synopsis: As Tommy is held captive by Mesogog, the teens work with Hayley to attempt to rescue him.
episodes.title: Legacy of Power

episodes.synopsis: Using Hayley's help and their new Raptor Cycles, the Dino Thunder Rangers storm the island base on a mission to rescue Tommy from Mesogog's clutches.
episodes.title: Back in Black

episodes.synopsis: Kira's old singing partner comes to town just as Mesogog releases the Donkeyvac monster, who sucks the youth from people and turns them old.
episodes.title: Diva in Distress

episodes.synopsis: Ethan is zapped into a video game.
episodes.title: Game On

episodes.synopsis: Trent's father purchases the café and threatens to fire Hayley to put Trent in charge, and Zeltrax releases a new creation to destroy the Rangers.
episodes.title: Golden Boy

episodes.synopsis: A new Dinozord Egg is uncovered by the Rangers during a class archeological dig, but Tyranodrones interfere, allowing Elsa to snag it first.
episodes.title: Beneath the Surface

episodes.synopsis: Nikki Valentina, star of the most popular TV show in the country, "Ocean Alert," visits Reefside while filming an episode of her show.
episodes.title: Ocean Alert

episodes.synopsis: Trent accidentally bonds with the White Dino Gem and becomes the White Dino Thunder Ranger.
episodes.title: White Thunder: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The evil White Ranger finds his own Dragozord Dino Egg and begins to bond it to him by feeding it energy from his Morpher.
episodes.title: White Thunder: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Tommy discovers the identity of the White Ranger.
episodes.title: White Thunder: Part 3

episodes.synopsis: Realizing he is the White Ranger, Trent quits his job in an attempt to protect his friends.
episodes.title: Truth and Consequences

episodes.synopsis: A strange meteorite lands in the forest, and its effects bring out repressed personality traits in anyone it comes in contact with.
episodes.title: Leader of the Whack

episodes.synopsis: Tommy, now freed from the amber, discovers he can't demorph from the form of Black Ranger.
episodes.title: Burning at Both Ends

episodes.synopsis: While helping Tommy clean up his lab, Kira stumbles onto a secret bone.
episodes.title: The Missing Bone

episodes.synopsis: A school bully sets his sights on Ethan. Meanwhile, Tommy discovers the true identity of Zeltrax.
episodes.title: Bully for Ethan

episodes.synopsis: When the wicked Mesogog attempts to restore Earth to a prehistoric age of dinosaurs, legendary veteran Ranger Tommy Oliver returns to action.
episodes.title: Lost and Found in Translation

episodes.synopsis: When Kira lands a new job as an intern on the Funky Fisherman cartoon show, Cassidy is dismayed to discover she was passed over.
episodes.title: It's a Mad Mad Mackerel

episodes.synopsis: As Anton Mercer explains to Trent that Mesogog was an experiment gone horribly wrong, Zeltrax creates the Copyotter to attack the city.
episodes.title: Copy That

episodes.synopsis: Zeltrax samples a portion of the new Evil White Ranger clone's energy and creates the White Terrorsaurus monster.
episodes.title: Triassic Triumph

episodes.synopsis: Kira is conflicted when the manager wants to shoot a music video with her, but wants her to compromise her own style.
episodes.title: A Star Is Torn

episodes.synopsis: While Elsa works on her plan to shoot a powerful laser beam at Jupiter, Kira and Ethan help Cassidy land a job at the TV station.
episodes.title: A Ranger Exclusive

episodes.synopsis: When Ethan takes an interest in deciphering the hieroglyphics of Egyptian ruler Tutenhawken, he accidentally frees an ancient evil.
episodes.title: Tutenhawken's Curse

episodes.synopsis: To help her mutant flower grow into the Thornox monster, Elsa uses a sample of a mysterious green slime.
episodes.title: Disappearing Act

episodes.synopsis: Tommy's invisibility problem is solved, but as a result, his Dino Gem is shattered and he ends up in a coma.
episodes.title: Fighting Spirit

episodes.synopsis: Conner gets involved with an environmentalist campaign to save a 100-year-old tree, all so he can impress a girl named Krista.
episodes.title: The Passion of Conner

episodes.synopsis: Ethan's cocky attitude concerning his skills at playing the Detonation Man computer game begins to get on everyone's nerves.
episodes.title: Isn't It Lava-Ly

episodes.synopsis: Upon discovering that two White Dino Thunder Rangers can't exist for much longer, the Evil White Ranger clone targets our heroes one last time.
episodes.title: Strange Relations

episodes.synopsis: When the Abyss of Evil is opened, Lothor returns and casts a spell on Shane, Tori and Dustin, turning them evil and setting them loose on Reefside.
episodes.title: Thunder Storm: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: In an attempt to help Shane, Tori and Dustin, Cam goes to the Abyss of Evil with Hunter and Blake to retrieve the Power Coins.
episodes.title: Thunder Storm: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Elsa begins to attack Elsa in her dreams.
episodes.title: In Your Dreams

episodes.synopsis: Trent is given a magical pen and accidentally pulls the Rangers into his comic book.
episodes.title: Drawn into Danger

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers discover the identities of Elsa and Mesogog.
episodes.title: House of Cards

episodes.synopsis: Through a series of clips, Conner, Kira and Ethan reminisce about how their lives have changed since becoming Power Rangers.
episodes.title: A Test of Trust

episodes.synopsis: Trent cuts a deal with Mesogog to spare Anton's life.
episodes.title: Thunder Struck: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: As Tommy rushes to rescue Elsa from Zeltrax, the Rangers stage one final battle against Mesogog.
episodes.title: Thunder Struck: Part 2
